// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1036 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 230ef514-0368-5d5e-bd7c-7d5167204dfb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
